				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Does anyone have any defense skill information?  A formula would do.  I want to keep my defense maxed out as I level, and I don't know how much defense I should have each level.  The most I could get it to at level 29 was 101 or 102.  Caster's Realm says that defense caps out at 155, which I am inclined to believe, but their formula per level is wrong unless Iksar defense progression is just weird.
